                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250217-52-off317 t18250217-52-cd318"></join>, two sheets, value 3 s., and a counterpane, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250217-52-victim363" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Garner
                     <interp inst="t18250217-52-victim363" type="surname" value="Garner"></interp>
